{"tid":2440821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西營盤健身室URSUS FITNESS增至十人染疫","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T09:04:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6f2c81c4cca12fe0af076aaa0d4d8f11024c6c","tid":2440821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】本港新增8宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，6宗屬本地感染，3宗源頭不明，初步確診約十多宗。薄扶林道一間健身中心增至十人染疫。<br />\n<br />\n3宗源頭不明都是昨日初步確診轉為確診，包括一名27歲男人，在薄扶林道64號一間健身室工作，周一交樣本後確診，健身室有九名顧客及工作人員亦初步確診。衞生防護中心正調查是否有關聯，呼籲曾在本月1至10日到訪該健身室的人盡快聯絡中心。<br />\n<br />\n一名26歲於觀塘賽馬會大樓心理衞生會樂道居殘疾人士院舍的活動助理，上月21日曾發燒，上周三到聯合醫院求醫，周一抽取樣本後確診；另一名是58歲男子居住在葵涌海峰花園1座，上周三發燒，潛伏期間曾到過至少10間餐廳用膳。<br />\n<br />\n另外，K11 MUSEA名潮食館群組再多兩名早前確診個案的同住家人染病，群組累計54人。"},{"pid":"4b930d0a8c7012ce70ba92934d09e6947c4b7c7a","tid":2440821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=426839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426839&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=a1574291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426839&h=0fa9ef53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=426839</a>"},{"pid":"bf31d18302031b0030500f0ecbd862ebe44bc45a","tid":2440821,"uid":76341,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"gym撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c9f0ae976728f52ad65637648b784082846962","tid":2440821,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f7d69d1f5abea73e8eed69f8583e2b6118b7cf","tid":2440821,"uid":2471,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"